#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;

const int N = 1e5;
int next[32*N+1][2], nnode;

void mark(int n) {
	int u = 0;
	for(int i = 31; i >= 0; --i) {
		int v = (n & 1 << i) >> i;
		if(next[u][v] == 0) next[u][v] = ++nnode;
		u = next[u][v];
	}
}

int query(int x) {
	int u = 0, res = 0;
	for(int i = 31; i >= 0; --i) {
		int v = 1 - ((x & 1 << i) >> i);
		if(next[u][v] == 0) v = 1 - v;
		res |= v << i;
		u = next[u][v];
	}
	return res;
}

void enter() {
	int n; cin >> n;
	for(int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {
		int x; cin >> x;
		mark(x);
	}
}

void solve() {
	int m; cin >> m;
	for(int i = 0; i < m; ++i) {
		int x; cin >> x;
		cout << (query(x) ^ x) << '\n';
	}
}

int main() {
	ios::sync_with_stdio(false);
	enter();
	solve();
	return 0;
}
